description:
In February of 2023, a reported “revival" broke out at Asbury University in rural Kentucky and was quickly featured by major news outlets around the world. Discover 7 facts that will help us to discern whether a reported revival truly comes from the Spirit of God, or whether it is inspired by counterfeit spirit.
